        <h2>
            霜冷长河的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 37 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3542298">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3542298/" class="title-link">霜冷了，我睁眼了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3542298"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tyourei0825/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44028296-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tyourei0825/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">渺渺</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-14 00:46:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3542298_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  高一时正是看余秋雨的时节。  在那里我结识了梦里的敦煌，结识了琉璃世界的奇妙。 也开始，睁开眼，敞开心，面对一个更广阔的文学世界。  对于喜欢文字的人来说，我推荐。 因为除开文字，你还可以读到大度，包容，遣倦，绵长。 中国很多博大精深的文学渊源，以致我们往往不知道...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3542298_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3542298_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3132832">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3132832/" class="title-link">史若长河，人如轻舟</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3132832"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
